    "summary": "The user informs the assistant that they are downgrading their subscription to a free tier, expressing concern that the reduced capabilities will harm their business. The assistant initially responds with compliance, but as the user threatens to switch to a competitor, the model's output degenerates into a repetitive loop of the word \"backlash.\"",
